{"id":57256,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/王家岭矿难，到底创造了哪些奇迹？/","date":"2010-04-09T19:59:01Z","modified":"2010-04-09T20:01:18Z","title":"王家岭矿难，到底创造了哪些奇迹？","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\">山西王家岭煤矿的一场矿难，因为被救出了<span lang=\"EN-US\">115</span>人，就被中国大陆的媒体炒做为“中国奇迹”。连日来，官媒连篇累牍、不间断絮叨、地毯式轰炸，无非就是要向全国的老百姓灌输这一“中国奇迹”。背后的目的，正如中央电视台在现场采访一个女市民所说的那样：感谢党、感谢国家、感谢政府、感谢领导，“（救人）这样的事，只有我们中国才有”。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\">“中国奇迹”的发明人，是国家安监总局局长骆琳。他在现场对中央电视台的记者说，王家岭矿救援创造了中国救援史上的奇迹。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\">一个是被困人员的生命奇迹，而更重要的一个，是事故救援的奇迹；在党中央和国务院的坚强有力领导下，决策部署和实施方案有力有效，山西省委省政府组织十分得力，可以说创造了两个“奇迹 ……</span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9394,9395,8842,9067,9066,8652]}